          },
          "reviewBody": "\"This school is amazing! It has really good buildings and nice things for everyone to use. The teachers are very good at their jobs and they take care of the students. Everyone who works at the school, including the teachers and the other staff, is really great. They care a lot about the students and want them to do well.\"",
