          "reviewBody": "A school where a child is not just a student but a school where the child is treated as an individual and is given the freedom ,guided freedom  to learn n grow at his/her pace.Overall care is taken and that helps the child to develop holistically.\nHappy to be a part of Vishwajyot Family.",
          "publisher": {
